summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Third Avenue No. from Aloha Street to the north line of Woodward Add. in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 18179, creating Local Improvement District No. 1713 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
